The paper discusses deep learning and its vulnerabilities to adversarial attacks, which are common in computer security (cs.CR) and computer vision (cs.CV) research. The paper also discusses countermeasures and defenses against these attacks, which are relevant to machine learning (cs.LG), artificial intelligence (cs.AI), and systems and control (cs.SI) research.
